    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @mdunbavan. Thanks for opening this issues.\r\n\r\nOne thing that I notice that makes your display empty is that there are no attributes in your records, just highlighted values. There must be something wrong in your index configuration (have you set some unretrievable attributes?).\r\n\r\nOn the IS.js part, it actually adds your template markup to the document for each of your result (and in your jsFiddle there is only one result).\r\n\r\nLet me know if I misunderstood something here.\r\n",
